### Regulatory and Compliance Requirements

**HIPAA Security Rule (45 CFR Part 164, Subpart C):** Applicable — MyClinic is a covered entity; OpenMRS processes ePHI. All HIPAA Security Rule safeguard requirements (administrative, physical, technical) apply.

**HIPAA Breach Notification Rule (45 CFR Part 164, Subpart D):** Applicable — unauthorized access to or disclosure of ePHI may trigger notification obligations to patients, HHS, and media (if breach affects 500+ individuals in a state).

