**NIST SP 800-53 Rev 5:** Selected as the security control framework. Controls are tailored to the HIGH impact baseline with additional controls selected based on threat environment and operational context.

**Business Associate Agreement:** Executed with AWS for HIPAA-eligible services. Executed with [LIS Provider name] for the laboratory information exchange.

